data.comment: The match is underway at Friends Arena.
Free kick for AIK in their own half.
In the minute 1, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Elfsborg.
Corner awarded to AIK.
AIK's Paulos Abraham is on target but unsuccessful.
In the minute 4, AIK have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
Ball goes out of play for a Elfsborg goal kick.
Bojan Pandzic awards the away team a throw-in.
In the minute 5, Throw-in AIK.
Free kick AIK.
Joseph Okumu is booked for the away team.
In the minute 7, AIK have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
AIK are coming forward and Daniel Granli gets in a strike, it misses the target, however.
Goal kick for Elfsborg at Friends Arena.
In the minute 9, AIK awarded a free kick in their own half.
Elfsborg's Johan Larsson breaks free at Friends Arena. But the strike goes wide of the post.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Solna.
In the minute 12, Corner awarded to AIK.
Bojan Pandzic signals a throw-in for Elfsborg, close to AIK's area.
Important block from the AIK defence as Frederik Holst fires in a strike for Elfsborg.
In the minute 16, Corner awarded to AIK.
Bojan Pandzic awards Elfsborg a goal kick.
Goal! Per Frick gives Elfsborg a 0-1 lead in Solna.
In the minute 20, Elfsborg have a goal kick.
Jesper Karlsson gets his shot on target but fails to score for Elfsborg.
Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.
In the minute 24, AIK awarded a free kick in their own half.
Elfsborg awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Free kick for Elfsborg in their own half.
In the minute 25, In Solna, Rami Kaib of Elfsborg is presented with a shooting opportunity. But the strike is blocked by the covering defence.
Elfsborg have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
Elfsborg's Per Frick gets in a shot but it is blocked by a AIK defender.
In the minute 28, Elfsborg have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
In Solna, Leo Vaisanen (Elfsborg) misses the target with a header.
Ball goes out of play for a AIK goal kick.
In the minute 29, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.
Bojan Pandzic signals a AIK throw-in in Elfsborg's half.
Henok Goitom (AIK) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In the minute 31, In Solna AIK drive forward through Daniel Granli. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Free kick for AIK in their own half.
Nabil Bahoui (AIK) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
In the minute 33, Per Frick (Elfsborg) gets booked by Bojan Pandzic, and will miss the next match due to the number of yellow cards received this season.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Throw-in for Elfsborg in their own half.
In the minute 36, Rami Kaib of Elfsborg smashes in a shot on target. The keeper saves, though.
Ball safe as Elfsborg is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.
In the minute 39, Elfsborg take a comfortable 0-2 lead thanks to Jesper Karlsson.
Simon Olsson with an assist there.
Elfsborg needs to be cautious. AIK have an attacking throw-in.
In the minute 41, It's a goal kick for the away team in Solna.
Per Frick for the away team is judged to be offside.
Bojan Pandzic blows to end the first-half.
In the minute 46, The second-half is underway in Solna.
Can AIK get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Elfsborg's half?
The home team have replaced Heradi Rashidi with Felix Michel Melki. This is the first substitution made today by Bartosz Grzelak.
In the minute 48, Throw-in for AIK at Friends Arena.
AIK have a goal kick.
Ball safe as AIK is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 49, Throw-in for AIK in their own half.
Throw-in for Elfsborg at Friends Arena.
Elfsborg awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 53, In Solna a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Free kick for Elfsborg in their own half.
Free kick for Elfsborg in the half of AIK.
In the minute 56, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Elfsborg.
Elfsborg's Jesper Karlsson gets his shot away but it misses the target.
Bojan Pandzic awards AIK a goal kick.
In the minute 57, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.
AIK to take a throw-in in Elfsborg territory.
Free kick for Elfsborg in the half of AIK.
In the minute 59, Stefan Silva is on a sub for Nabil Bahoui for AIK.
Goal kick for AIK at Friends Arena.
The home team replace Rasmus Lindkvist with Eric Kahl.
In the minute 61, Corner awarded to AIK.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Solna.
Throw-in for AIK in the half of Elfsborg.
In the minute 63, Eric Kahl of AIK gets in a strike, but is off target.
Goal kick for Elfsborg at Friends Arena.
In Solna AIK's Stefan Silva is caught offside.
In the minute 65, AIK will need to be alert as they defend a dangerous free kick from Elfsborg.
Elfsborg drives forward and Jesper Karlsson gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
In Solna a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 67, AIK awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Throw-in AIK.
Can AIK capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Elfsborg's half?
In the minute 70, AIK have a dangerous throw-in.
AIK push forward at Friends Arena and Henok Goitom gets in a great header. The attempt is cleared by the Elfsborg defence.
Bojan Pandzic signals a AIK throw-in in Elfsborg's half.
In the minute 71, It's getting dangerous! Free kick for AIK close to the penalty box.
AIK push forward at Friends Arena and Sebastian Larsson gets in a strike. This is blocked, however, by a determined Elfsborg defence.
Paulos Abraham (AIK) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In the minute 73, Throw-in high up the field for AIK in Solna.
Sivert Heltne Nilsen is writhing in pain and play has been suspended for a few moments.
AIK are pushing forward but Eric Kahl's finish is wide of the goal.
In the minute 74, Elfsborg have a goal kick.
Samuel Holmen is replacing Simon Olsson for the away team.
Sivert Heltne Nilsen, who was grimacing earlier, has been substituted. Robert Gojani is the substitute for Elfsborg.
In the minute 75, Elfsborg make their third substitution with Gustav Henriksson replacing Joseph Okumu.
Can AIK get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Elfsborg's half?
Free kick in a good position for Elfsborg!
In the minute 77, Jesper Karlsson is down and play has been interrupted for a few moments.
Elfsborg's Johan Larsson gets in a shot on goal at Friends Arena. But the effort is unsuccessful.
Jesper Karlsson is back on his feet again.
In the minute 78, Elfsborg awarded a free kick in their own half.
Bojan Pandzic awards the away team a throw-in.
AIK to take a throw-in in Elfsborg territory.
In the minute 81, Throw-in for AIK close to the penalty box.
Free kick for Elfsborg in their own half.
It seems as if Jesper Karlsson is unable to continue. Simon Strand replaces him for the away team.
In the minute 82, Corner awarded to Elfsborg.
Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.
Throw-in Elfsborg.
In the minute 84, Free kick AIK.
Bojan Pandzic awards the away team a throw-in.
Throw-in high up the field for AIK in Solna.
In the minute 86, Ball goes out of play for a Elfsborg goal kick.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
AIK pushes forward through Paulos Abraham, whose finish on goal is saved.
AIK have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
In Solna AIK attack through Eric Kahl. The finish is off target, however.
In the minute 88, Bojan Pandzic awards Elfsborg a goal kick.
In the minute 88, The home team replace Bilal Hussein with Panajotis Dimitriadis.
Throw-in for AIK in the half of Elfsborg.
Henok Goitom strikes to reduce the deficit to 1-2 at Friends Arena.
In the minute 89, Great play from Stefan Silva to set up the goal.
Elfsborg awarded a free kick in their own half.
Throw-in for AIK at Friends Arena.
Bojan Pandzic will wait an extra 5 minutes before blowing the whistle to end the 2nd half.
Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.
AIK have a dangerous throw-in.
Bojan Pandzic signals a throw-in for AIK, close to Elfsborg's area.
Free kick for Elfsborg in their own half.
AIK awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Ball goes out of play for a Elfsborg goal kick.
AIK awarded a free kick in their own half.
Free kick for Elfsborg in their own half.
It's 1-2 as the referee blows for full-time.
AIK's Eric Kahl has been booked in Solna and will miss the next match through suspension.
Deniz Hummet is on a sub for Rasmus Alm for Elfsborg.
